HEADWORD: Sang-froid
<hw>Sang`-froid"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F., cold
blood.]</ety> <def>Freedom from agitation or excitement of mind;
coolness in trying circumstances; indifference; calmness.</def>
<rj><au>Burke.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
